Compiling KOffice with cmake

We use the snapshop of kdelibs4, for the time being.
The url is:

svn.kde.org/home/kde/branches/work/kdelibs4_snapshot

Make sure this has compiled and installed completely; especially
the $kdedir/share/apps/modules/cmake directory must be installed

It is sufficient to set PATH and LD_LIBRARY_PATH to the location
of your kde4 library installation to compile: running is more
demanding.

then type

cmake .

in the toplevel dir and after that, make
